      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in a state that mirrors its original delivery day. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free from the typical road rash, swirl marks, or door dings found on even well-kept used examples. It has been exclusively garage-kept and protected with a high-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats are firm and devoid of bolster wear or creasing, and the interior still carries a clean, fresh scent. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive binder documenting every service interval performed by certified technicians. There are no leaks, no rattles, and the engine delivers smooth, effortless power. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to acquire an example that has been pampered with an obsessive level of care and attention to detail.",
