      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an uncompromising 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in showroom condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering peak torque through six individual throttle bodies and a precision Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The double-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to ensure long-term structural rigidity. Mechanical integrity is paramount, with a linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline and a factory-spec limited-slip differential providing exceptional corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut, complemented by perfectly preserved bushings and a flawless underside. This is a collector-grade example for the purist who demands mechanical perfection and analog feedback.",
